  <entry>
    <title>3月6日天梯赛选拔1补题（牛客周赛94,97）</title>
    <link href="/2026/03/14/3%E6%9C%886%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A9%E6%A2%AF%E8%B5%9B%E9%80%89%E6%8B%941%E8%A1%A5%E9%A2%98/"/>
    <url>/2026/03/14/3%E6%9C%886%E6%97%A5%E5%A4%A9%E6%A2%AF%E8%B5%9B%E9%80%89%E6%8B%941%E8%A1%A5%E9%A2%98/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="题目链接"><a href="#题目链接" class="headerlink" title="题目链接"></a>题目链接</h1><ul><li><a href="https://ac.nowcoder.com/acm/contest/110696/B">牛客周赛94 B - 小苯购物</a></li><li><a href="https://ac.nowcoder.com/acm/contest/110696/C">牛客周赛94 C - 小苯的与三角形</a></li><li><a href="https://ac.nowcoder.com/acm/contest/110696/D">牛客周赛94 D - 小苯的序列染色</a></li><li><a href="https://ac.nowcoder.com/acm/contest/112078/C">牛客周赛97 C - 移动</a></li><li><a href="https://ac.nowcoder.com/acm/contest/112078/E">牛客周赛97 E - 平衡排列</a></li></ul><hr><h1 id="B-小苯购物"><a href="#B-小苯购物" class="headerlink" title="B - 小苯购物"></a>B - 小苯购物</h1><h2 id="问题描述"><a href="#问题描述" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><p>有 3 个优惠券，每个优惠券有两个参数 <code>a</code>、<code>b</code>：</p><ul><li>当当前商品价格 <strong>≥ a</strong> 时，可以减少 <code>b</code> 元。</li></ul><p>每个优惠券 <strong>最多使用一次</strong>，且可以选择 <strong>使用或不使用</strong>。</p><p>给定商品初始价格 <code>n</code>，求最终价格的 <strong>最小值</strong>。</p><hr><h2 id="考察知识点"><a href="#考察知识点" class="headerlink" title="考察知识点"></a>考察知识点</h2><ul><li>暴力枚举</li><li>全排列</li></ul><hr><h2 id="题解思路"><a href="#题解思路" class="headerlink" title="题解思路"></a>题解思路</h2><p>由于优惠券只有 <strong>3 张</strong>，可以直接 <strong>枚举使用顺序</strong>。</p><p>使用 <code>next_permutation</code> 枚举所有排列，依次模拟使用优惠券的过程即可。</p><p>每次更新当前最小价格。</p><hr><h2 id="代码实现"><a href="#代码实现" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; n;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> a[<span class="hljs-number">3</span>][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>];<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="hljs-number">3</span>; i++) cin &gt;&gt; a[i][<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] &gt;&gt; a[i][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> res = n;<br>    vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; tp = &#123;<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, <span class="hljs-number">2</span>&#125;;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">do</span><br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> t = n;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; <span class="hljs-number">3</span>; i++)<br>        &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(t &gt;= a[tp[i]][<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]) t -= a[tp[i]][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>        &#125;<br>        res = <span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(res, <span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0LL</span>, t));<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">next_permutation</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">ALL</span>(tp)));<br>    cout &lt;&lt; res &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="C-小苯的与三角形"><a href="#C-小苯的与三角形" class="headerlink" title="C - 小苯的与三角形"></a>C - 小苯的与三角形</h1><h2 id="问题描述-1"><a href="#问题描述-1" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><p>给定一个整数 <code>x</code>，需要找到一个最小的 <code>y (1 ≤ y &lt; x)</code>，</p><p>使得 <code>x</code>、<code>y</code>、<code>x &amp; y</code> 三个数可以构成 <strong>三角形</strong>。</p><p>若不存在这样的 <code>y</code>，输出 <code>-1</code>。</p><hr><h2 id="考察知识点-1"><a href="#考察知识点-1" class="headerlink" title="考察知识点"></a>考察知识点</h2><ul><li>位运算</li><li>二进制性质</li><li>数学分析</li></ul><hr><h2 id="题解思路-1"><a href="#题解思路-1" class="headerlink" title="题解思路"></a>题解思路</h2><p>由于：</p><figure class="highlight gml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gml"><span class="hljs-variable language_">x</span> &amp; <span class="hljs-variable language_">y</span> ≤ <span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(<span class="hljs-variable language_">x</span>, <span class="hljs-variable language_">y</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>因此 <code>x &amp; y</code> 一定是三个数中 <strong>最小的一个</strong>。</p><p>三角形成立需要满足：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css">(<span class="hljs-attribute">x</span> &amp; <span class="hljs-attribute">y</span>) + <span class="hljs-attribute">y</span> &gt; <span class="hljs-attribute">x</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>考虑 <code>x</code> 的 <strong>最高位二进制</strong>：</p><ul><li><p>如果 <code>y</code> 在该位为 <code>0</code><br>则 <code>x &amp; y</code> 和 <code>y</code> 在这一位都没有贡献，无法超过 <code>x</code>。</p></li><li><p>如果 <code>y</code> 在该位为 <code>1</code><br>则 <code>(x &amp; y) + y</code> 在这一位会产生进位，一定大于 <code>x</code>。</p></li></ul><p>因此最小的 <code>y</code> 就是：</p><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">x</span> 的最高位对应的 <span class="hljs-number">2</span> 的幂<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>特殊情况：</p><p>如果 <code>x</code> 本身就是 <strong>2 的幂</strong>，则不存在合法 <code>y</code>。</p><hr><h2 id="代码实现-1"><a href="#代码实现-1" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; x;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> t = x;<br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> res = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(t /= <span class="hljs-number">2</span>) res &lt;&lt;= <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(res == x) cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">-1</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> cout &lt;&lt; res &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="D-小苯的序列染色"><a href="#D-小苯的序列染色" class="headerlink" title="D - 小苯的序列染色"></a>D - 小苯的序列染色</h1><h2 id="问题描述-2"><a href="#问题描述-2" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><p>给定一个长度为 <code>n</code> 的二进制字符串 <code>t</code>，初始时 <strong>全为 0</strong>。</p><p>可以进行任意次操作：</p><ul><li>选择任意 <strong>三个连续位置</strong></li><li>将其赋值为 <code>&quot;110&quot;</code></li></ul><p>给定目标字符串 <code>s</code>，问是否可以通过若干次操作将 <code>t</code> 变为 <code>s</code>。</p><hr><h2 id="考察知识点-2"><a href="#考察知识点-2" class="headerlink" title="考察知识点"></a>考察知识点</h2><ul><li>构造</li><li>字符串性质</li><li>贪心观察</li></ul><hr><h2 id="题解思路-2"><a href="#题解思路-2" class="headerlink" title="题解思路"></a>题解思路</h2><p>观察操作 <code>&quot;110&quot;</code> 的性质：</p><ol><li><p>每次操作 <strong>最后一位一定是 <code>0</code></strong><br>因此最终字符串 **最后一位不能是 <code>1</code>**。</p></li><li><p>去掉前导 <code>0</code> 后，剩余部分必须是 **连续的一段 <code>1</code>**。</p></li></ol><p>如果第一个 <code>1</code> 后面出现 <code>0</code>，则无法通过操作构造出来。</p><p>满足上述条件即可构造成功。</p><hr><h2 id="代码实现-2"><a href="#代码实现-2" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; n;<br>    string s;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; s;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(s[s.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>() - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] != <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>)<br>    &#123;<br>        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;NO&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++)<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(i == n - <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>        &#123;<br>            cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;YES&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(s[i] == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(s[i] == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;1&#x27;</span>)<br>        &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(s[i + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>] == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>) cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;NO&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot;YES&quot;</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="C-移动"><a href="#C-移动" class="headerlink" title="C - 移动"></a>C - 移动</h1><h2 id="问题描述-3"><a href="#问题描述-3" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><p>给定一个长度为 <code>n</code> 的字符串，由 <code>.</code> 和 <code>#</code> 组成：</p><ul><li><code>#</code> 表示障碍</li><li><code>.</code> 表示可通行</li></ul><p>现在有 <code>q</code> 次查询，每次给定两个位置 <code>x</code> 和 <code>y</code>，允许无视一次 <strong>任意长度的连续障碍</strong>，问：</p><blockquote><p>要从 <code>x</code> 移动到 <code>y</code>，最少需要无视的障碍长度是多少？</p></blockquote><hr><h2 id="考察知识点-3"><a href="#考察知识点-3" class="headerlink" title="考察知识点"></a>考察知识点</h2><ul><li>二分查找</li><li>前缀&#x2F;障碍位置记录</li><li>贪心 + 查询优化</li></ul><hr><h2 id="题解思路-3"><a href="#题解思路-3" class="headerlink" title="题解思路"></a>题解思路</h2><p>暴力方法检查每次路径的障碍会超时。</p><p>优化做法：</p><ol><li><strong>记录所有障碍的位置</strong>到数组 <code>a</code>。</li><li>对于每次查询 <code>[x, y]</code>：<ul><li>使用 <code>lower_bound</code> 找到左端障碍</li><li>使用 <code>upper_bound</code> 找到右端障碍</li></ul></li><li>如果左右迭代器指向同一位置，说明区间内没有障碍，无需无视，答案为 <code>0</code>。</li><li>否则，计算 <strong>右障碍 - 左障碍 + 1</strong> 即为最少需要无视的连续障碍长度。</li></ol><p>时间复杂度：</p><ul><li>预处理障碍：O(n)</li><li>每次查询：O(log k)，k 为障碍总数</li><li>总体：O(n + q log n)</li></ul><hr><h2 id="代码实现-3"><a href="#代码实现-3" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n, q;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; n &gt;&gt; q;<br>    string s;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; s;<br>    vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; a;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; (<span class="hljs-type">int</span>)s.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>(); i++)<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(s[i] == <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;#&#x27;</span>) a.<span class="hljs-built_in">push_back</span>(i + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(q--)<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x , y;<br>        cin &gt;&gt; x &gt;&gt; y;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> l = <span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(x, y);<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> r = <span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(x, y);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">auto</span> it_r = <span class="hljs-built_in">upper_bound</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">ALL</span>(a), r);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">auto</span> it_l = <span class="hljs-built_in">lower_bound</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">ALL</span>(a), l);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(it_r == it_l)<br>        &#123;<br>            cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        it_r --;<br>        cout &lt;&lt; *it_r - *it_l + <span class="hljs-number">1</span> &lt;&lt; endl; <br>    &#125;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="E-平衡排列"><a href="#E-平衡排列" class="headerlink" title="E - 平衡排列"></a>E - 平衡排列</h1><h2 id="问题描述-4"><a href="#问题描述-4" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><p>定义一个排列 <code>p</code> 为 <strong>平衡排列</strong>，当且仅当存在一个索引 <code>mid</code> 使得：</p><p>$$<br>\sum_{i&#x3D;1}^{mid} p_i &#x3D; \sum_{i&#x3D;mid+1}^{n} p_i<br>$$</p><p>现给定 <code>n</code>，请构造一个长度为 <code>n</code> 的平衡排列。</p><p>若不存在这样的排列，输出 <code>-1</code>。</p><hr><h2 id="考察知识点-4"><a href="#考察知识点-4" class="headerlink" title="考察知识点"></a>考察知识点</h2><ul><li>贪心构造</li><li>数学性质</li><li>子集和</li></ul><hr><h2 id="题解思路-4"><a href="#题解思路-4" class="headerlink" title="题解思路"></a>题解思路</h2><p>若要满足两侧和相等，则整个排列的总和必须为偶数。</p><p>排列 <code>1..n</code> 的总和为：</p><p>$$<br>S &#x3D; \frac{n(n+1)}{2}<br>$$</p><p>若 <code>S</code> 为奇数，则无法分成两个相等的部分，直接输出 <code>-1</code>。</p><p>若 <code>S</code> 为偶数，则目标是构造一组数使其和为：</p><p>$$<br>\frac{S}{2}<br>$$</p><p>可以采用贪心策略：</p><p>从 <code>n</code> 到 <code>1</code> 依次遍历，如果当前数字加入左侧不会超过目标值，就放入左侧，否则放入右侧。</p><p>最终将左侧与右侧拼接即可得到满足条件的排列。</p><hr><h2 id="代码实现-4"><a href="#代码实现-4" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; n;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>((n * (n + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) / <span class="hljs-number">2</span>) % <span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<span class="hljs-comment">//不#define int long long 会超时</span><br>    &#123;<br>        cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">-1</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span>;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> s = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> mid = n * (n + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) / <span class="hljs-number">4</span>;<br>    vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; l, r;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = n; i &gt;= <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i--)<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(s + i &lt;= mid)<br>        &#123;<br>            l.<span class="hljs-built_in">push_back</span>(i);<br>            s += i;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> r.<span class="hljs-built_in">push_back</span>(i);<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">reverse</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">ALL</span>(r));<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; (<span class="hljs-type">int</span>)l.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>(); i++) cout &lt;&lt; l[i] &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; (<span class="hljs-type">int</span>)r.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>(); i++) cout &lt;&lt; r[i] &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-string">&quot; &quot;</span>;<br>    cout &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr>]]></content>
    
    
