  <entry>
    <title>3月8日牛客周赛补题</title>
    <link href="/2026/03/11/3%E6%9C%888%E6%97%A5%E7%89%9B%E5%AE%A2%E5%91%A8%E8%B5%9B%E8%A1%A5%E9%A2%98/"/>
    <url>/2026/03/11/3%E6%9C%888%E6%97%A5%E7%89%9B%E5%AE%A2%E5%91%A8%E8%B5%9B%E8%A1%A5%E9%A2%98/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>C、D、E 共三题</p><hr><h1 id="题目链接"><a href="#题目链接" class="headerlink" title="题目链接"></a>题目链接</h1><ul><li><a href="https://ac.nowcoder.com/acm/contest/129231/C">牛客周赛124 C - Unique Number</a></li><li><a href="https://ac.nowcoder.com/acm/contest/129231/D">牛客周赛124 D - Balanced Array</a></li><li><a href="https://ac.nowcoder.com/acm/contest/129231/E">牛客周赛124 E - Maximize The Sum</a></li></ul><hr><h1 id="C-Unique-Number"><a href="#C-Unique-Number" class="headerlink" title="C - Unique Number"></a>C - Unique Number</h1><h2 id="问题描述"><a href="#问题描述" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><p>对给定序列 <code>c[n]</code>（初始所有值为 0）进行如下操作：</p><ul><li>选择一个前缀 <code>[1, i] (1 ≤ i ≤ n)</code></li><li>将前缀中所有元素的值增加 <code>1</code></li></ul><p>同时，你还会得到一个 <strong>限制序列</strong> <code>d[n]</code>。</p><p>要求在操作过程中 <strong>任意时刻</strong></p><p>$$<br>c_i \le d_i<br>$$</p><p>最终能使序列 <code>c</code> 中 <strong>不同数值的种类数最多是多少</strong>？</p><hr><h2 id="考察知识点"><a href="#考察知识点" class="headerlink" title="考察知识点"></a>考察知识点</h2><ul><li>贪心</li><li>构造</li><li>单调序列</li></ul><hr><h2 id="题解思路"><a href="#题解思路" class="headerlink" title="题解思路"></a>题解思路</h2><p>要使 c 中不同数值种类数最大，最终构造的数组应该是<strong>单调递减</strong>的。因为每次操作只能增加前缀，越靠后的位置被增加的次数越少，所以最终值满足 $c_1$ ≥ $c_2$ ≥ … ≥ $c_n$。</p><p>构造策略如下：</p><ol><li>从第一个位置开始，取最大可能值 $c_1$ &#x3D; $d_1$</li><li>对于第 i 个位置，考虑前一个值 $c_{i-1}$：<ul><li>如果 $c_{i-1}$ - 1 ≤ $d_i$，则可以取 $c_i$ &#x3D; $c_{i-1}$ - 1</li><li>如果 $c_{i-1}$ - 1 &gt; $d_i$，则只能取 $c_i$ &#x3D; $d_i$</li></ul></li><li>每确定一个值，种类数 +1</li><li>当构造到 $c_i$ &#x3D; 0 时，后面所有位置都只能是 0，此时退出循环</li></ol><p>不需要真正构造出整个数组，只需要模拟这个过程计数即可。</p><hr><h2 id="代码实现"><a href="#代码实现" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; n;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; <span class="hljs-title">d</span><span class="hljs-params">(n)</span></span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) cin &gt;&gt; d[i];<br>    <span class="hljs-comment">//没有要求给出完整排列，不用创建 c 数组</span><br>    <br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> cnt = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>, now = d[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<span class="hljs-comment">//cnt计不同数值种类，now可看作d[i-1]</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++)<br>    &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(now == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>        &#123;<br>            cnt++;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(now - <span class="hljs-number">1</span> &lt;= d[i])now --;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(now - <span class="hljs-number">1</span> &gt; d[i]) now = d[i];<br>        cnt++;<br>    &#125;<br>    cout &lt;&lt; cnt &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="D-Balanced-Array"><a href="#D-Balanced-Array" class="headerlink" title="D - Balanced Array"></a>D - Balanced Array</h1><h2 id="问题描述-1"><a href="#问题描述-1" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><p>你有一个长度为 <code>n</code> 的数组 <code>a</code>。</p><p>定义一个子数组 $a_l$, $a_{l+1}$, …, $a_r$</p><p>是 <strong>平衡的</strong>，当且仅当满足：</p><p>$$<br>\max(a_l, …, a_r) - \min(a_l, …, a_r) \le 1<br>$$</p><p>求有多少个整数对 <code>(l, r)</code> 满足：</p><figure class="highlight basic"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs basic"><span class="hljs-symbol">1 </span>≤ l ≤ r ≤ n<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>且子数组是平衡的。</p><hr><h2 id="考察知识点-1"><a href="#考察知识点-1" class="headerlink" title="考察知识点"></a>考察知识点</h2><ul><li>滑动窗口</li><li>双指针</li><li>map维护区间信息</li></ul><hr><h2 id="题解思路-1"><a href="#题解思路-1" class="headerlink" title="题解思路"></a>题解思路</h2><p>使用 <strong>滑动窗口</strong>。</p><p>维护区间 <code>[j,i]</code>：</p><ul><li>使用 <code>map</code> 统计出现次数</li><li>当出现以下情况时移动左端点 <code>j</code></li></ul><p>非法情况：</p><ol><li><p>不同元素种类超过 <code>2</code></p></li><li><p>最大值与最小值差值大于 <code>1</code></p></li></ol><p>当窗口合法时：</p><figure class="highlight apache"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs apache"><span class="hljs-attribute">res</span> += (i - j + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>表示以 <code>i</code> 为右端点的所有合法子数组。</p><hr><h2 id="代码实现-1"><a href="#代码实现-1" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; n;<br>    <span class="hljs-function">vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; <span class="hljs-title">a</span><span class="hljs-params">(n + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>)</span></span>;<br>    map&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>, <span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; mp;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> res = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>, j = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>; i &lt;= n; i++)<br>    &#123;<br>        cin &gt;&gt; a[i];<br>        mp[a[i]]++;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span>(j &lt; i &amp;&amp; mp.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>() &gt; <span class="hljs-number">2</span> || (mp.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>() == <span class="hljs-number">2</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="hljs-built_in">abs</span>(mp.<span class="hljs-built_in">begin</span>()-&gt;first - mp.<span class="hljs-built_in">rbegin</span>()-&gt;first) &gt; <span class="hljs-number">1</span>))<br>        &#123;<br>            mp[a[j]]--;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(mp[a[j]] == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) mp.<span class="hljs-built_in">erase</span>(a[j]);<br>            j++;<br>        &#125;<br>        res += (i - j + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>    &#125;<br>    cout &lt;&lt; res &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr><h1 id="E-Maximize-The-Sum"><a href="#E-Maximize-The-Sum" class="headerlink" title="E - Maximize The Sum"></a>E - Maximize The Sum</h1><h2 id="问题描述-2"><a href="#问题描述-2" class="headerlink" title="问题描述"></a>问题描述</h2><p>有长度为 <code>n</code> 的 <strong>二进制数组</strong> <code>a</code>。</p><p>可以进行如下操作：</p><p>选择三个连续位置</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css"><span class="hljs-selector-tag">i</span> , <span class="hljs-selector-tag">i</span> + <span class="hljs-number">1</span> , <span class="hljs-selector-tag">i</span> + <span class="hljs-number">2</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>设原值为：</p><figure class="highlight css"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs css"><span class="hljs-attribute">x</span>, <span class="hljs-attribute">y</span>, z<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>变换为：</p><figure class="highlight gml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs gml"><span class="hljs-variable language_">x</span>* = <span class="hljs-variable language_">x</span> ⊕ <span class="hljs-variable language_">y</span><br><span class="hljs-variable language_">y</span>* = <span class="hljs-variable language_">y</span> ⊕ z<br>z* = z ⊕ <span class="hljs-variable language_">x</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>经过若干次操作后，数组所有元素之和的最大可能值是多少？</p><hr><h2 id="考察知识点-2"><a href="#考察知识点-2" class="headerlink" title="考察知识点"></a>考察知识点</h2><ul><li>异或</li><li>状态分析</li><li>构造</li></ul><hr><h2 id="题解思路-2"><a href="#题解思路-2" class="headerlink" title="题解思路"></a>题解思路</h2><p>枚举三元组变化：</p><table><thead><tr><th>原状态</th><th>新状态</th><th>1数量变化</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>000</td><td>000</td><td>+0</td></tr><tr><td>001</td><td>011</td><td>+1</td></tr><tr><td>010</td><td>110</td><td>+1</td></tr><tr><td>100</td><td>101</td><td>+1</td></tr><tr><td>011</td><td>101</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>101</td><td>110</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>110</td><td>011</td><td>0</td></tr><tr><td>111</td><td>000</td><td>-3</td></tr></tbody></table><p>为了让 <code>1</code> 尽可能多：</p><ul><li><code>2~4</code> 可以 <strong>增加1</strong></li><li><code>5~7</code> 可以 <strong>互相转换</strong></li><li><code>1</code> 和 <code>8</code> 无用</li></ul><p>只要数组中存在 <code>1</code>，就能不断把 <code>0</code> 变成 <code>1</code>。</p><p>最终 <strong>最多剩下一个 0</strong>。</p><hr><h2 id="代码实现-2"><a href="#代码实现-2" class="headerlink" title="代码实现"></a>代码实现</h2><figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cpp"><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">solve</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; n;<br>    map&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>, <span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; mp;<br>    string s;<br>    cin &gt;&gt; s;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>; i &lt; n; i++) mp[s[i] - <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>]++;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(mp[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) cout &lt;&lt; n &lt;&lt; endl;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(mp[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) cout &lt;&lt; <span class="hljs-number">0</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> cout &lt;&lt; n - <span class="hljs-number">1</span> &lt;&lt; endl;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
